dnight blue, black and silver, with the mic itself having Bluetooth support, four pickup patterns for speech an adjustable stand as well as a simple plug-and-play setup.Hey, did you know? CNET Deals texts are free, easy and save you money. Best Amazon deals Logitech/CNET It seems like everyone has a podcast or a YouTube channel these days. If you want to hop on that bandwagon, you'll definitely need a good microphone. This deal isn't the lowest-ever price we've seen for the Logitech Blue Yeti model, but it's still a decent price cut, with savings of $32. It's available in midnight blue, black or silver. The Yeti works just as well for Zoom meetings. Keurig/CNET For some folks, that early morning coffee is essential, and this Keurig K-Express is a fine companion. Not only is it easy to fit into a small kitchen, but it's also small enough to put in a bag, so if you travel a lot, you can always have fresh coffee. It can brew in three sizes -- 8-, 10- or 12-ounce cups -- and comes with a 42-ounce reservoir.  Kasa/CNET These Kasa Mini smart plugs are an easy and affordable way to add some serious convenience to your home. They allow you to turn your devices on or off from anywhere using your phone, or create an automated schedule based on your daily routines. Plus, you can even control them hands-free with Siri, Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant (with a compatible smart speaker or display). Samsung/CNET If you're looking for a budget-friendly monitor that has a decent display, several ports and a game mode, then this 22-inch Samsung S33A is worth considering. It's on sale for $74, giving you $41 in savings.  More Amazon deals worth checking out:TP-Link AX3000 Wi-Fi 6 router: $85 (save $15)Razer Huntsman Mini 60% gaming keyboard: $80 (save $40)Beats Pill x Kim Kardashian Bluetooth speaker: $100 (save $50)Oral-B iO Deep Clean electric toothbrush: $60 (save $40)Baseus USB-C docking station: $20 (save $20)JBL Go 3: $30 (save $10)Soundcore P20i wireless earbuds: $20 (save $20)